# GRAPHICS::GET_STATUS_OF_TAKE_MISSION_CREATOR_PHOTO

## Summary
Call this after calling BEGIN_TAKE_MISSION_CREATOR_PHOTO to check when the operation has finished, and whether it succeeded

## Returns
* **PHOTO_OPERATION_STATUS**
